title: Koffie&Koffie
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Bakery, European, Dutch, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee bar, lunch food and sweets. Offers a spelt cappuccino which is vegan, and vegan sweets might be raspberry cocoa bars, banana bread, and chocolate bars. Has non-dairy milk like almond milk and soy milk for coffee drinks.
